<div id="index-heading">
  <br>
  <h1 class="center">Social Funding for ill children.</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <% @featured.each do |f| %>
      <div class="four columns">
        <div class="panel">
          <%= image_tag('/assets/uploads/' + f.photo, style: 'width: 300') %><br>
          <h5 class="center"><%= link_to f.name, f %></h5>
          <p><%= f.bio[0..250] %>...</p>
          <%= link_to "Learn more about #{f.name}", f %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row"  style="background: url('/assets/hands.png') 0 0px no-repeat; background-position: right top;">
  <br>
  <div class="six columns" style="min-height: 350px">
    <h1>What is Fund3Lives?</h1>
    <p style="text-align: justify">
      Fund3lives aims to help 3 different beneficiaries that needs funding through the use of internet. Fund3lives will introduce 3 major beneficiaries at the same time that need immediate assistance. On fund3lives, the beneficiary needs to reach his/her funding goal before the date that the he/she requested. If the funding does not reach its goal, all the donations will be given directly on your chosen beneficiary.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<br>
<div class="row">
  <div class="six columns offset-by-six">
    <h1>Who is Fund3Lives?</h1>
    <p style="text-align: justify">
      Fund3lives is the brainchild of Ken-Lauren Daganio and Onin Malasan, when they joined Webgeek's Devcup Hackathon.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


